<P>
   KOCH-DETECTIVES (Wichita, Kan.) _ One of America's wealthiest
and most private families found itself in an unwanted spotlight
last summer as its fractious members waged a bitter courtroom fight
over the family business, Koch Industries, the vast oil and gas
company with headquarters on the prairie at the edge of town here.
By Douglas Frantz.
