<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-28 15:10 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7069 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u f &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-DAIRY-QUEEN-BOS &LR;      07-28 1413
