</P>
<P>
   07-29 NYSE VOLUME -- 25p6 x 2 7/8 -- Volume on the NYSE.
</P>
<P>
   07-29 KEY RATES -- 12p6 x 3 -- Treasury bonds, notes and bills.
</P>
<P>
   07-29 ARROWS -- 22p6 x 1 1/2 -- Market performance indicators.
