<DOCTYPE> MISCELLANEOUS TEXT (slug-filter) </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-28 15:19 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7098 &Cx1f; tie-z
u a &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-CIRCUITS-BUDGET-NYT &LR;      07-28 0431
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-CIRCUITS-BUDGET-NYT </SLUG>
  
