with the House aimed at producing a final juvenile justice bill. By
GREG McDONALD.
</P>
<P>
   AMMO-CLIPS (Washington) _ Sen. Dianne Feinstein suffers a defeat
when the Senate rejected her legislation that would have banned the
import of high-capacity ammunition clips. Feinstein had argued that
hunters and sports shooters weren't interested in the clips and
that only criminals wanted them. By JUDY HOLLAND.
</P>
