decision to bypass the committee process and go straight to the
floor with a GOP managed-care proposal, Augusta Republican Charlie
Norwood will likely have a direct confrontation with his leaders as
he tries to convince his fellow Republicans to support the type of
managed-care reform he wants. Also, the Medical Association of
