   &QR;  TV comedy: ``Pee-wee's Playhouse,'' Volumes 1-16, $12.95 each,
or in two sets: Volumes 1-8, and Volumes 9-16, $99.92 each.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  History: ``D-Day: The Total Story,'' the History Channel,
three-volume set, $39.95.
</P>
<P>
   &QR;  Kids: Barney: ``Let's Play School!'' VHS, $14.95, DVD, $24.99.
</P>
<P>
   _Steve Murray
</P>
