<P>
   FBC-SEC-MEDIADAYS _ BIRMINGHAM, Ala. _ The offseason has been a
troubled one for coach Tommy Tuberville and the Auburn Tigers.
First, there was the highly-criticized decision to drop the
season-opening football game at Florida State and that was followed
by a decision to release six players from their scholarship. All of
this followed a frustrating 1998 season which saw coach Terry
Bowden resign and interim coach Bill Oliver sue the university
after he wasn't given the job. (Barnhart, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 20.
</P>
