<P>
   FBC-COLLEGE-PREVIEW _ It's obvious to see that college football
season is on the horizon when the preseason magazines hit the
newsstands during the summer. Athlon's, Street and Smith's and the
Sporting News are just a few of the many magazines that preview
college football. Most of the magazines favor Florida State this
year while others like Penn State. What is the process used by
magazines staffs to determine their No. 1 teams? A look at the
process, what some of the top-ranked teams think about the ranking,
etc. (Barnhart, Cox News Service) MOVED.
