<P>
   BUSH-LATINOS _ WASHINGTON _ Gov. George W. Bush of Texas, who
declined an invitation by La Raza to speak at its national
convention this week, has also recently declined other invitations
to speak to Hispanic and other minority groups. The groups'
reaction and the possible political import. (Heath, Cox News
Service).
</P>
