breakfast chatter, morning programs like ``GMA'' and ``Today''
enjoy growing clout _ and audience -- within network news
divisions. By Don Aucoin.
</P>
<P>
   MUSIC-CALDWELL (Boston) _ Sarah Caldwell announces she's
returning to her home state of Arkansas to teach. By Richard Dyer.
800 words.
</P>
