plans to move for use by NYTimes News Service clients, AMs and PMs
of July 29, 1999, and thereafter. The stories will carry the ``f''
financial news category code unless otherwise noted. For questions
about stories, please contact Stewart Slavin at the Daily News,
(818) 713-3701.
