 San Francisco _ WATER _  Ponds and other water features are among
the fastest-growing garden trends. With a little planning and
minimal upkeep, they provide spots of tranquillity that invite
visitors to relax.
 &HT;    With optional sidebars: Water plants for the garden, Where to
learn more, Where to find water features and supplies. 
 By Janet Fletcher  
 c. 1999 The San Francisco Chronicle  
