<DOCNO> NYT19990728.0372 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-07-28 19:33 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7556 &Cx1f; tad-z
u w &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-GORE-LARAZA29-COX     07-28 0719
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-GORE-LARAZA29-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Gore targets GOP tax cut and Bush at La Raza convention
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (p) political categories.
 &HT;    By Scott Shepard
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
