Weaver, 44, has ministered to hundreds of track employees, jockeys,
grooms, trainers and racing fans. ``I really didn't want to go into
the ministry,'' he says. ``God just about had to send a lightning
bolt with a note on it in order for me to get the picture.'' There
are 39 racetrack chaplains nationwide.( D. Fahleson/Houston
Chronicle Photo)
